Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Industrial Design Build Opportunity. Up to 30,000 SF to be built, with potential for units ranging from 5,000 SF and up. Building is planned to include 2 dock level and 2 drive in doors, with potential to add more to suit your needs. Potential to build with up to 30 ft. clear height. Located at the corner of Cuddy Blvd and Artisans Cres., just northeast of Veteran's Memorial Pkwy. Public transit stop in front of the Property with additional routes available via Oxford Street. Price starts at $8.25 PSF Net, subject to construction pricing and Tenant's Specifications/Space Plans. Additional rent is an estimate, subject to final costing and confirmation of Property Taxes.
